Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we be off, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FRIEREN: BEYOND JOURNEY'S END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[cart wheels rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren sighs] It's unusually\Nwarm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] It is. I'll take\Nthe bonus warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would prefer\Nsome cold, hard cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] Four measly coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to look for work\Nin the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even\Ngotten there yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're thinking\Nabout work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we stay two steps ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our journey will come\Nto a premature end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So work it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we find\Nsomething suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] Thank you very much\Nfor the ride, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[COACHMAN] Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not every day I have\Na first-class mage in my cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could breathe easy,\Nthanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness. You'll be on the road\Nto Ende for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most folks would never dare\Nventure so far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of us in that camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a journey like yours\Nsounds unimaginably long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] Maybe it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[♪ opening theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FRIEREN: BEYOND JOURNEY'S END
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(477,39)\bord0\shad0}{\fs13}29 years after the death of Himmel the Hero, in\Nthe Saum Marshes, located in the Northern Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Uh? [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much,\Nbut I caught one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] I'll add it\Nto our breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.\NI already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[rustling]\N-[FRIEREN] Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be\Naround here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too early for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up curious\Nabout something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And curiosity knows no clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You praised her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling\Nit was a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] That's a pretty stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what makes it so special?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't conjure fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] It's called\Na magic-nullifying crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mineral that\Nneutralizes magical effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NA specimen of this purity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has an effective radius\Nof three meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stark, step over there for me,\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an extremely rare find.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it were pebble-sized,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be worth\Nseveral pieces of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crystal this large\Ncould buy us a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great,\Nbut it blocks our magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Travelling with it would\Nrender us completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it and we're\Ndead men walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Tis the burden we bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't bear it.\NPlease get rid of the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a monster attacked right now,\Nwe'd all be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. But it would be\Na shame
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to leave it without sharing\Nits flashiest property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly a terrific show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you imbue these stones\Nwith a large amount of mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]...they glow\Nwith an impressive light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] It's blinding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN]\NJust throw that thing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Keep up our pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll reach\Nthe next village today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally getting close\Nto the Northern Plateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plateau is very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still must venture\Nthrough a vast forest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and volcanic area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A volcanic area?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like we're in\Nfor some real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NI wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been\Nan eruption in centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, it's a relatively\Nsafe hot spring region.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hot spring sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like\Nit's been a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I had a warm bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're long overdue\Nfor some rest and relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] Strange.\NStop for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The earth here\Nis exceptionally thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[rumbling]\N-[Stark screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've stumbled\Nupon an underground cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground of a marshland\Ncan never be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Mistress Frieren?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Land rump first.\N-[STARK] Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] No wonder we found\Nthat magic-nullifying crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen\Na deposit this large before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Please get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cave is practically filled\Nto the brim with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we brought it\Nall back with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd be rich as kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we're not\Nup to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic-nullifying crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of the hardest materials\Nin existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and unlike most stones\NI've encountered,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can neither be cut\Nnor processed using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NSome treasures of nature
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are simply\Nout of humanity's reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we're not climbing\Nour way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for another exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting\Non you now, Stark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't use magic\Nto defend ourselves, down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're helpless young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't forgiven\Nyour "old hag" quip
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the dragon duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expert grudge-holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK]\NWhen I imagined our journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never pictured camping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-in a place like this.\N-[Frieren snores]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] This cave complex\Nis immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not fond of the number\Nof animal bones we've found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Mistress Frieren,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this might be the den\Nof a giant monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed she can\Nsleep so soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK]\NNot a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] Even down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she still seems\Nto be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm far too afraid to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even detect mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so isolated and helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I've been plunged\Ninto total darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[loud rumbling]\N-[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frieren? Wake up! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NA venomous apex dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venomous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terrible matchup\Nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die from poison again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't die the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't matter.\NI've got to fight it, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were\Ndrooling like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-How could you sleep so--\N-I could sleep so soundly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I trust you\Nwith my life, Stark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling\Nsolidified within me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the very moment I recruited you\Nto be our warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A party can't function properly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without complete\Nand utter trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you trust someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose only skill\Nis running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a choice,\NI would run right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we run away together then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stark, Fern,\Nplease close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[EISEN] Himmel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly trust me\Nwith your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I question your sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[HIMMEL] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[EISEN] Your faith should\Nnot be so easily won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[EISEN]\NI abandoned my village and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. If you want to run,\Nwe can run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[EISEN] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a party.\NWe'll follow where you lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Eisen scoffs, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Himmel sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running sounds like a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scoundrel! You took the pebble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and left the priest\Nwith the boulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the pebble will complain\Nyou stink of liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Himmel chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But running away as a team\Nisn't so miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark continues panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NShall we be off, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Frieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get my legs\Nto take another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 29: SHALL WE GO, THEN?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,29 YEARS AFTER THE DEATH\NOF HIMMEL THE HERO,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IN THE GREAT SANFT FOREST,\NLOCATED IN THE NORTHERN LANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK]\NWill this be enough for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have\Npicked some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!\NI'm the first one back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was too quick\Nwith the gathering, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it wouldn't hurt\Nto get some fishing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bag a big one\Nthis time. I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren shivering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] So cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] We'll reach\Nthe hot springs soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Good as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was given to you\Nby Stark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirrored-lotus bracelet\Nis quite the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also cleaned off\Nthe hairpin you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All bright and shiny again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're careful\Nwith your staff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to relish the ritual
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of maintaining\Nyour equipment, Fern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been smiling\Nthis whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Fern chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] Maybe I care so much\Nbecause they were gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from my home to the objects\Nthat filled it, to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a part of me\Njust cherishes the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to own things\Nwith meaning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was\Nwell worth the headache
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,picking it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took you a long time\Nto choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[chuckles]\N-[rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea the two of you\Nwould be bathing, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there. All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How confounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I alone in feeling\Nan awkward tension in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally\Nstarting to pick up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the more\Ntouchy-feely stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some major growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] This seems to happen\Nwith some frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you two\Nare simply ill-matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK]\NI wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Stark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NIf you're uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can always just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be in this party\Nto begin with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I hadn't forced you\Nto join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't forced me?\NThat's not why I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN]\NWe're at a crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] It seems this path\Nleads to the Northern Plateau,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Neutral Harbor\Nlies down the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frieren, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that look like an inn\Nto you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN] This is\Na frequently traveled road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least we won't have\Nto camp out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[bell dinging]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[WIRBEL] Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[FRIEREN] Hm?\N-[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems our reunion came\Nsooner than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Stark,\Nthanks again for your help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that Fresser business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, Wirbel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, I decided\Nto travel home by sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News from the north is dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demons are acting up\Nin the far reaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get up there\Nas fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with these two
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until we make it to the capital,\Nthat is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's anxious about seasickness.\NThe whining's incessant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Na grown man, Wirbel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far too old for whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I thought I was still in\Nthe full flower of my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only a recent departee\Nfrom my twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Funny. All you old guys\Nsuffer from the same delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[WIRBEL] Anyway, Stark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had time to think\Nabout my proposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation up north has gone\Nfrom bad to worse, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reliable front-line fighters\Nare in serious demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we could really use\Nyour axe, Stark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a few years\Nuntil things stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I told you before,\NWirbel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My services\Nhave been pledged already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not in my nature\Nto give up easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes\Nto the safety of the north,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Frieren.\NCan I work on him a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Wait--\N-You may do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[WIRBEL] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Frieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[ALL] Cheers.\N-[Wirbel chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, Stark,\NI'm a fun guy to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\NSeems he's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[SCHARF] Indeed.\N-[STARK] Appreciate the offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's a nice\Nchange of pace for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stark must find our party\Nsomewhat restrictive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[WIRBEL]...coins\Nand maidens' hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Yeah, that doesn't sound\Nlike my kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I turned down Wirbel's offer,\Nif that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN] Are you certain?\NYou don't have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think either of you\Nrealize why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you\Nand Frieren, I was at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see\Nthe meaning in it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told,\NI was ready to cut and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that village\Nto fend for itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frieren doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's under the impression
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she forced me\Nto join this party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against my will.\NBut she's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just met. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK] Your encouragement\Nrelit a fire in me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that had been cold\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that moment, I knew\Nthe right thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're just too modest\Nto have noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Frieren isn't\Nthe only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my cowardly hide is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stark chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise\NI'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Fern chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[soft thudding]\N-[Ferns gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please try\Nand be nicer to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Stark.\NTime for head pats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[exclaims] What evil\Nare you plotting? Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FERN]\NWhat a pain in the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Frieren snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[breathing shakily]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Fern blows]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[WIRBEL] I guess I couldn't\Nconvince you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three should take the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would save you valuable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean travel\Nis a tad too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master's party trekked\Nthrough the Northern Plateau,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so will we.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Fern chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always accepting odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And landing ourselves\Nin all manner of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detours are a part\Nof our process.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[chuckles] You've carved out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,quite the adventurous path\Nfor yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won't block it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll reach\Nthe far north eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But until then, you take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we be off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[♪ closing theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[STARK]\NThat seems a bit extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[EISEN] Talk about tyrannical.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[HEITER] Or maybe your joy\Nmerely grows with our sorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[HERO OF THE SOUTH] I'll die\Nwithout achieving my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[HIMMEL]\NAt least we defeated a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[FRIEREN]\N"That's the Hero of the South."
